                            <comment id="17464705" author="klease78" created="Thu, 23 Dec 2021 17:01:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, I didn&apos;t get to it before the 3.14 release. I will deprecate the option in the definitions. I could already remove it from the reifiers and processors since it has no effect anyway. Is that OK with you, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davsclaus&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davsclaus&quot;&gt;davsclaus&lt;/a&gt; ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
